<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/401558-is-this-book-fiction-or-non-fiction-i">Is this book fiction or non-fiction? I took it out of the library and it seemed more like it was a novel &quot;based on&quot; historical events than a book of history.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_401558'><a id="like_count_community_question_401558" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/401558?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F15801668-the-girls-of-atomic-city">like</a></span>

